@startuml
title Quiz Lifecycle - State Diagram

[*] --> Pending : quiz created\nnow < availableFrom

Pending --> Available : current time reaches start
Pending --> Missed : deadline passes before attempt

Available --> Attempted : student submits quiz
Available --> Missed : current time > deadline

Attempted --> [*]
Missed --> [*]

state Pending {
  note right
  Quiz visible to matching
  section/course student
  but cannot be attempted yet
  end note
}

state Available {
  note right
  Student can open and submit
  quiz before deadline
  end note
}

state Attempted {
  note right
  Further attempts are blocked
  and score is shown in history
  end note
}

state Missed {
  note right
  Deadline expired with no attempt
  end note
}
@enduml
